<p>The <b>video game industry</b> (formally referred to as <b><a href="/wiki/Interactive_entertainment" title="Interactive entertainment">interactive entertainment</a></b>) is the <a href="/wiki/Economics" title="Economics">economic</a> sector involved with the <a href="/wiki/Video_game_developer" title="Video game developer">development</a>, <a href="/wiki/Marketing" title="Marketing">marketing</a> and sale of <a href="/wiki/Video_game" title="Video game">video games</a>. It encompasses dozens of job disciplines and employs thousands of people worldwide.</p>
