<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Video_game_industry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://groups.google.com/group/comp.games.development.industry/topics?hl=en&amp;lnk" class="external text" title="http://groups.google.com/group/comp.games.development.industry/topics?hl=en&amp;lnk" rel="nofollow">comp.games.development.industry</a> (<a href="/wiki/Google_Groups" title="Google Groups">Google Groups</a>)</li>
